{"tid":2220704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實班蚑那狗講嘢都自相矛盾","createTime":"2020-09-28T00:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T06:11:58.000Z","uid":48234,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a6fb009b4510a4b5a84483b06954e6f21f56cd39","tid":2220704,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T00:16:31.000Z","msg":"甴近平: 中国永遠不稱霸，永遠不擴張<br />\n小粉紅:<br />\n「台灣是中国不可分割的一部份」<br />\n「你違反一個中国原則」<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母台灣而家擺撚明係一個獨立運作緊嘅國家嚟<br />\n永遠不擴張?<br />\n咁你做乜撚嘢想侵略台灣?<br />\n做乜撚嘢翻牆出去搞人?<br />\n翻牆出去搞人<br />\n迫人跟你哋班玻璃心蚑那狗嘅意見<br />\n根本係另一種侵略其他國家嘅行為<br />\n又話人哋干涉你哋內政，你哋又干涉人內政?<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">總結:甴近平講大話講撚到出晒面<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"e2de152ac3cdade09d2902830ec6c9d296ef2428","tid":2220704,"uid":132525,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T01:15:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"653dc61233659dcd16c273a3f56e035d52c06e23","tid":2220704,"uid":48234,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e2de152ac3cdade09d2902830ec6c9d296ef2428","tid":2220704,"uid":132525,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T01:15:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T01:18:55.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">復出啦?低級撩交嗌嘅奶共狗<br />\n連登日報&mdash;支持獨裁政權者，無權享有言論自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1180589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1180589</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XNv9jui.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXNv9jui.jpg&h=2d820456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請問魯班七號(狗隻#132525)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2088497\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2088497</a><br />\n魯班七號(狗隻#132525)俾人屌就玩反彈屌返人，點知佢大撚把痛腳俾人捉撚住<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2125003\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2125003</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"8a0c957464da45a32b66dce81b75e1a1435